==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quercite
<hw>Quer"cite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A
white crystalline substance, <chform>C6H7(OH)5</chform>, found in
acorns, the fruit of the oak (<gen>Quercus</gen>). It has a sweet taste,
and is regarded as a pentacid alcohol.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quercitin</ent>⟦br⟧
